Highlights
                    

                      

                        
M1 | interz - 1vs2 MP9 clutch (CT - pre-plant situation)

                      

                      

                        
M1 | s1mple - 3 quick M4A1-S kills on the Mid defense (initial frags - anti-eco)

                      

                      

                        
M2 | electronic - 3 quick M4A1-S kills (2 HS) on the bombsite A defense (vs mostly pistols)

                      

                      

                        
M2 | B1T - 3 AK kills (2 HS) on the bombsite A defense

                      

                      

                        
M2 | Ax1Le - 1vs2 clutch (T- bomb planted after 1 clutch kill)

                      

                      

                        
M2 | B1T's 1vs3 clutch attempt (T - post-plant) is denied by the final CT (sh1ro)

                      

                      

                        
M3 | Hobbit's 1vs4 clutch attempt is denied by the final CT (Perfecto) in the post-plant situation

                      

                      

                        
M3 | Perfecto - 3 quick AK HS kills on the bombsite B defense (clean round - vs mostly TEC9s)

                      

                      

                        
M3 | s1mple - 3 P250 kills (2 HS) on the bombsite B bomb plant defense (3vs3 situation - second half pistol round)
